world.bentobox.bentobox.blueprints.dataobjects

Class BlueprintBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • world.bentobox.bentobox.blueprints.dataobjects.BlueprintBundle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataObject

    public class BlueprintBundle
extends Object
implements DataObject
    Represents a bundle of three Blueprints. This is what the player will choose when creating his island.

    1.5.0
